title: Twisted: The Untold Story of a Royal Vizier - Official Soundtrac
description:
The official soundtrack from Twisted - The Untold Story of a Royal Vizier

Twisted was performed on July 2013, in Chicago, IL by the musical theatre company Starkid. The musical is a Wicked style parody of the 1992 Disney film Aladdin, telling the story from the point of view of Jafar, the Royal Vizier.

Recordings are 128 kbps, recorded in a studio by the cast
